      "def_destin": "270150:2606099273",
      "def_action": "replace",
      "actionlist": [
        {
          "provenance_ref": "404",
          "action_order": 0,
          "from": ["weaponpics/1.6/*.png"],
          "from_type": "file",
          "into": ["media/packages/GFL_Castling/textures/"],
          "into_type": "path",
          "comment": {
            "string1": "对象中没有`destin`或者`action`属性",
            "string2": "因此使用mod对象`270150:3428584891`也就是其亲代的`def_destin`和`def_action`作为值",
            "string3": "`destin`是`270150:2606099273`, `action`是`replace`",
            "string4": "`270150:2606099273`拆开看, `270150`是`RunningWithRifles`, `2606099273`是它的模组`GFL_Castling`",
            "string5": "在steam库中, mod以数字content_id的形式管理, 因此`270150:2606099273`就是`steamapps/workshop/content/270150/2606099273/`",
            "string6": "`replace`的意思是直接复制过去, 不管原本存不存在",
            "string7": "用shell解释就是`cp -r steamapps/workshop/content/270150/3428584891/weaponpics/1.6/*.png steamapps/workshop/content/270150/2606099273/textures/`, 但是硬盘文件这类I/O操作需要调用系统API提高效率",
            "string8": "`replace`类`action`必须有有效的`from`与`into`属性, 以便于知道从哪里复制文件到哪里去, 否则为无效操作, 此时报告, 记录, 下一条"
          },
          "sidecar_ref": "404"
        },
        {
          "provenance_ref": "404",
          "action_order": 0,
          "destin": "270150:2606099273",
          "action": "replace",
          "from": ["weaponpics/1.7/*.png"],
          "from_type": "file",
          "into": ["media/packages/GFL_Castling/textures/"],
          "into_type": "path",
          "comment": {
            "string1": "这个对象明确指定了`destin`和`action`, 因此以它自己的`destin`和`action`为准",
            "string2": "`destin`是`270150:2606099273`, `action`是`replace`",
            "string3": "用shell解释就是`cp -r steamapps/workshop/content/270150/3428584891/weaponpics/1.7/*.png steamapps/workshop/content/270150/2606099273/textures/`",
            "string4": "你可能想问既然destin和replace跟亲代一样为什么要多此一举",
            "string5": "这是为了说明, 只有未指定`destin`和`action`的对象才会使用亲代的默认值, 一旦指定了自己的`destin`和`action`, 就完全不管亲代的默认值了, 以自己的为准",
            "string6": "因此这个对象虽然跟亲代的默认值一样, 但它的`destin`和`action`是它自己的, 现在不受亲代的默认值影响, 以后也不会"
          },
          "sidecar_ref": "404"

        },
