          "comment": {
            "string1": "这个对象的`destin`是`270150:0`, 这意味着它的目标是游戏base文件`steamapps/common/RunningWithRifles`",
            "string2": "这个对象的`action`是`create`, 这意味着它要创建一个新文件",
            "string3": "`create`与`replace`的区别在于, `aggregated_rule_set.json`的作者使用`create`有意告诉你, 那个位置“之前不该有文件”",
            "string4": "如果没有文件, 那么皆大欢喜, 用shell解释就是 `cp steamapps/workshop/content/270150/3428584891/weaponpics/castears_kawaii.png steamapps/common/RunningWithRifles/media/textures/castears_kawaii.png`",
            "string5": "如果已经有文件了呢？该怎么办？向日志中添加一条:",
            "string6": "yyyymmddHHMMSS 创建`castears_kawaii.png`前已经于`steamapps/common/RunningWithRifles/media/textures/`发现同名文件",
            "string7": "然后执行的操作用shell解释就是 `cp steamapps/workshop/content/270150/3428584891/weaponpics/castears_kawaii.png steamapps/common/RunningWithRifles/media/textures/castears_kawaii.png`",
            "string8": "如此处理之后, 虽然不符合预期, 但无论是记录日志, 还是把文件放在指定位置上, 都完成了, 因此继续干后面的事情去"
          },
          "sidecar_ref": "404"
        }
