            "string11": "用shell解释即`cp -r steamapps/workshop/content/270150/modder_will_name_this_local_mod_whatever_as_their_will/reqingyouhao/media/wsmxswrp.yaml steamapps/workshop/content/270150/2606099273/media/packages/GFL_Castling/hotkeys.xml`",
